location.fullValue: The Kingshill Plan, High Pointe View

data.description: Immaculate, quality ALL BRICK townhome with seasonal views of the lake is yours to own at 1950 Buford Dam Rd Unit 103! This brick beauty is minutes from parks, shopping, restaurants, and medical facilities! Stroll through the sidewalk lined streets and charming brick courtyard where the gorgeous leaded glass door greets you. Inside a formal front entrance greets you with views into the fireside family room that has all new sliding doors to make it even more inviting! Freshly installed luxury vinyl flooring throughout the home makes it carpet free and maintenance free. Fresh paint, updated lighting, 4 year old roof and transferable warranty are some of the many owner upgrades throughout. Two story great room has marble fireplace, gas logs, built in bookshelves, wall of windows and leads to the 4 seasons covered patio. Patio has sliding doors and insulated floor for year round enjoyment and views of the lake with complete privacy! Kitchen includes stained cabinets, stainless steel appliances, brand new dishwasher, glass cabinets and granite counters. Eat in dining area is open and overlooks the fireside family room. This upscale open floor plan continues with an Owners Suite on the main level. Tall ceilings, plantation shutters, double vanity bathroom and separate tub/shower all make the primary suite a dream. Upstairs a massive loft overlooks the family room with two more bedrooms. Each bedroom is large with private bathrooms and large closets. Downstairs features another MASSIVE flex space, perfect for theatre, workout room, office or teen suite. Workshop is an added bonus! Two car garage is extra deep for storage and has flat driveway for ease. From the upgrades, move in ready feel to the year round views of the water and minutes from Lanier this home is a DREAM!
